Package: smallset
Title: R package to create Smallset timelines for compact and clear communication of data preprocessing steps
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Lydia",
           family = "Lucchesi",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "Lydia.Lucchesi@anu.edu.au")
Description: The package takes R data preprocessing code and turns it into a Smallset timeline, a visualisation of data preprocessing steps. The Smallset timeline aims to support transparency and accessibility in research dissemination.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
